{
  "id": "adv_event_2301_01_05_02",
  "title": "飛躍の年、無敵のLizNoir",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "別事務所のプロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-betupro002.m4a",
      "text": "神崎莉央が加わって、さらにスコアが上がってる！？\nだ、ダメだ……こんなの、勝てる訳がない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio Kanzaki joining in has raised the score even further!?\nOh…no… There's no way we can win against this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.800013982,
      "endTime": 12.3666806486,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13100.000000000002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16866.666666600002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osakcountlivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osakcountlivestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.6333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirはⅢXのレコードを塗り替え",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――LizNoir has rewritten IIIX's record‚ and",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.700013982,
      "endTime": 17.200013982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osakcountlivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osakcountlivestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.200013982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大阪での合同カウントダウンライブは幕を閉じた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the joint countdown live in Osaka has come to a close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.200013982,
      "endTime": 21.000013982000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osakcountlivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osakcountlivestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.0333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.2666806486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　莉央さん\nさっきまで警察にいたんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? Rio-san‚\nwere you at the police just a while ago!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3333473153,
      "endTime": 27.523090973499997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.7333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "一体何をやっちゃったんですか？\nこころが許してあげますから、罪を告白して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What on earth did you do?\nPlease confess‚ Kokoro will forgive you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7333473153,
      "endTime": 35.2590325866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.4666806486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "あのねぇ……。私の母が倒れている人を助けたの\nその人、線路に落ちそうになって大事故になりかけたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… You see‚ my mother helped someone who had collapsed.\nThat person was about to fall onto the tracks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4666806486,
      "endTime": 45.6014710042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.800013982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "それで、母が事情聴取を受けることになったんだけど\n迎えに行った私まで、警察の方に引き留められて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ my mother had to be questioned by the police‚ and even\nI‚ who went to pick her up‚ got detained by the police…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.800013982,
      "endTime": 53.693608103900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "説得するのに時間がかかってしまったの。ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It took some time to persuade them. I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.900013982,
      "endTime": 57.919583188199994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.1333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ、スリクスのレコードを更新出来たし\n莉央と莉央のお母さんも無事なら、僕は満足だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. We were able to update ⅢX's record‚ and\nif Rio-chan and her mother are both safe‚ I'm satisfied.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1333473153,
      "endTime": 65.9414773966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.1333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよね！　こんな大きな会場のレコードを\n塗り替えたなんて、凄いことですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! Updating the record at\nsuch a big venue is amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1333473153,
      "endTime": 72.9857375679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.1666806486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "それもこれも、新センターこころのおかげですね～\nこれでもう、スリクスを倒したも同然です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And it's all thanks to the new center‚ Kokoro.\nWith this‚ it's as good as defeating ⅢX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1666806486,
      "endTime": 80.9443969628,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11633.333333399989
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.1333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、今回は本当に助かったわ。……あら？\n星見プロのみんなから勝利祝いのメッセージが届いてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes‚ I'm really grateful this time… Huh?\nEveryone from Hoshimi Prods is sending congrats messages.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1333473153,
      "endTime": 91.1085247893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.8666806486
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.300013982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとだ！　凄く沢山来てますね\nあ、スリクスのkanaさんからも届いてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! There are so many messages coming in.\nOh‚ there's even a message from kana-san from ⅢX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.300013982,
      "endTime": 97.8148504658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.000013982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "彼女、なんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What does she say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.000013982,
      "endTime": 99.96668060889999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.1666806486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "えっと――過去のkana達に勝ったからって\n調子のんなし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well――She says something like‚\n\"Don't get cocky just because you beat us in the past.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1666806486,
      "endTime": 105.5276885086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.200013982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "すぐにまたkana達がレコードを上書きするから\nLizNoirなんて敵じゃないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kana will overwrite your record again soon.\nI don't see LizNoir as an enemy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7333473153,
      "endTime": 111.17857080569999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.3666806486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスは強気ですね～\nそれと、愛ちゃんの物真似もなかなかですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ⅢX is quite confident‚ huh~\nAlso‚ Ai-chan's impersonation is quite good~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3666806486,
      "endTime": 117.98511822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.200013982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "彼女なりの勝利祝いなんじゃない？\n誰かさん達に似て、素直じゃなさそうだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe that's her way of celebrating victory?\nShe doesn't seem straightforward .like someone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.200013982,
      "endTime": 125.0543864697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.9666806486
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.9333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "誰のこと言ってるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2333473153,
      "endTime": 126.74497992469999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.0333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "それはもちろん莉央さんのことじゃないですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ we're talking about you‚ Rio-san~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0333473153,
      "endTime": 131.1454107709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.3333473153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_05-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "……二人とも自覚がないんだね。ま、いいか",
      "translations": {
